1.0.0.a2:
August 28th 2016.
2nd alpha.
- Conversations are no longer located on a separated JID. Everything is under the main JID.
- Conversations can now be aliased. Exemple: 107233005422865236837@hangups.example.net can now be aliased as
  my_conf@hangups.example.net, which is more recognizable on the client sides. This is done by implementing XEP-0050.
- Various bugfixes.

1.0.0a:
December 12th 2015.
first Alpha.